# Terraform Provider {{ .ProviderName | title }}

A Terraform provider for managing resources via the [Waldur](https://waldur.com/) API.

## Requirements

- [Terraform](https://www.terraform.io/downloads.html) >= 1.0
- [Go](https://golang.org/doc/install) >= 1.24 (to build the provider plugin)

## Installation

### From Terraform Registry

```hcl
terraform {
  required_providers {
    {{ .ProviderName }} = {
      source = "waldur/{{ .ProviderName }}"
    }
  }
}
```

## Provider Configuration

```hcl
provider "{{ .ProviderName }}" {
  # Endpoint and token are optional if environment variables are set
  # endpoint = "https://your-waldur-instance.com/api/"
  # token    = "your-api-token"
}
```

| Argument | Description | Required | Default |
|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| `endpoint` | The {{ .ProviderName | title }} API endpoint URL | No | `WALDUR_API_URL` env var |
| `token` | API authentication token | No | `WALDUR_ACCESS_TOKEN` env var |

